  {
    "title": "Union of Skills: One year of concrete action to keep Europe competitive",
    "link": "https://employment-social-affairs.ec.europa.eu/news/union-skills-one-year-concrete-action-keep-europe-competitive-2026-03-05_en",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-05T09:06:51.000Z",
    "content": "<p>5 March 2026 marks the 1st anniversary of the Union of Skills, a flagship initiative to make Europe more competitive. It has delivered concrete action, supporting workers and businesses, reinforcing cooperation with Member States, industry and education providers and building a governance framework.</p>",
    "creator": "",
